structure.unit: A CABINET FOR HEALTH AND FAMILY SERVICES

law.catch_line: Promulgation of administrative regulations to implement KRS 194A.600 to 194A.609.
law.text: The cabinet shall promulgate administrative regulations under KRS Chapter 13A sufficient to implement KRS 194A.600 to 194A.609.
law.history: Created 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 6, sec. 6, effective July 14, 2000.
